{"tid":962021,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[電影百科] 一齊講下唔同國家有咩國寶級演員","createTime":"2018-12-30T14:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T19:14:31.000Z","uid":209051,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"eac0f7172b73488a3006baa5dc3c2d81242ed1ea","tid":962021,"uid":209051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"香港/美國嗰啲大路嘅唔使講啦，想認識下世界唔同國家有咩公認有實力/地位崇高嘅演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男女都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好有啲冷門啲嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己本身都唔係話睇好多戲，所以識嗰啲都係出名啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋下磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  :<br />\n法國: Jean Dujardin <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/89/fa/61/89fa61376249d301741ac8237d4b811c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F89%2Ffa%2F61%2F89fa61376249d301741ac8237d4b811c.jpg&h=4933939c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代表作: The Artist (2011) <br />\n奧斯卡史上首位法籍影帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n西班牙: Javier Bardem<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Premios_Goya_2018_-_Javier_Bardem.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Ff%2Ff5%2FPremios_Goya_2018_-_Javier_Bardem.jpg&h=b5912062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代表作: Before Night Falls (2000)，The Sea Inside (2004)，No Country For Old Men (2007)<br />\n西班牙第一位奧斯卡金像獎得主<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢做痴線佬好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n印度: Aamir Khan<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.tribuneindia.com/cms/gall_content/2018/10/2018_10$largeimg30_Tuesday_2018_122429398.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.tribuneindia.com%2Fcms%2Fgall_content%2F2018%2F10%2F2018_10%24largeimg30_Tuesday_2018_122429398.jpg&h=513565eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代表作: 3 idiots (2009)，PK (2014)，Secret Superstar (2017)<br />\n外號「印度劉德華」，曾被《時代雜誌》稱為「印度的良心」<br />\n<br />\n以色列: Gal Gadot<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f2/Gal_Gadot_by_Gage_Skidmore_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Ff%2Ff2%2FGal_Gadot_by_Gage_Skidmore_2.jpg&h=f31063b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代表作: Fast &amp; Furious系列，Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice (2016)，Wonder Woman，Justice League (2017)<br />\n2012年4月，媒體網站《Shalom Life》評選出的「50位全球最有天賦、最聰穎、最有趣及最高雅的猶太女性」中，被列為第五名<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n憑《神奇女俠》和《正義聯盟》而成為2017年票房最高的女星，以及該年度票房第三高的演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你哋仲識邊啲可以講下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb33092f38d9b818722a7caf24822d7f0b56a80f","tid":962021,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"成龍"},{"pid":"781f13cfc35760b9db0685e675faa85d01d03f3c","tid":962021,"uid":56999,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.renminbao.com/rmb/article_images/2012-10-18-121018wjb01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.renminbao.com%2Frmb%2Farticle_images%2F2012-10-18-121018wjb01.jpg&h=cee947dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1faaabff808184d026ab5718890b5b2d4fc9d513","tid":962021,"uid":209051,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"781f13cfc35760b9db0685e675faa85d01d03f3c","tid":962021,"uid":56999,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.renminbao.com/rmb/articl